          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "NCWidgetSearchViewDelegate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " protocol defines methods that enable user searches in the search view controller of a Today widget. The "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/notificationcenter/ncwidgetsearchviewcontroller/1449562-delegate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " of an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/notificationcenter/ncwidgetsearchviewcontroller"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " must adopt the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/notificationcenter/ncwidgetsearchviewdelegate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " protocol."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The search view controller tells its delegate to perform a search on a user’s input and the delegate returns the results by setting the controller’s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/notificationcenter/ncwidgetsearchviewcontroller/1449551-searchresults"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property. The search view controller also tells its delegate when a user clears the search field or chooses a search result, so that the delegate can prepare for a new search or dismissal."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
